{"tid":2723,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【求屌醒】我，係一個廢青。","createTime":"2016-11-26T01:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T09:27:05.000Z","uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5143a6659034008a95a2e3202680434b5eaad55e","tid":2723,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"學歴只有中六畢業<br />\n單親家庭跟老母，所以完全無男人味，只有怕事既毒撚性格<br />\n把口又唔得<br />\n無專長<br />\n又唔靚仔<br />\n興趣只有打機<br />\n窮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返緊份濕鳩工，身邊既人一直都叫我搵份可以長遠發展既工，但我又唔知自己做得d咩。<br />\n<br />\n每次有人勸我都覺得自己好無用，身邊既朋友都開始有自己既目標，而我仲係戇戇鳩鳩咁⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n今日個心情就好似今日個天咁灰⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b751fa505f399daeb46194386722e80316c7f9","tid":2723,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:08:00.000Z","msg":"廢乜撚野青<br />\n自己開心咪得<br />\n點解要理人點睇？"},{"pid":"32118834a2a7a91b1be461853f07ad3cc8c62cc0","tid":2723,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢乜撚野青<br />\n自己開心咪得<br />\n點解要理人點睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一諗到將來就⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc85f2db12fcf9b735af949c07d77698bdbcc33b","tid":2723,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:18:00.000Z","msg":"好你少少 讀緊19degree 但都係廢青"},{"pid":"c5f4587c290eb5a9686cec4cee60b821da1506e6","tid":2723,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:18:18.000Z","msg":"自己諗啦<br />\n冇年幫到你，靠自己"},{"pid":"0171ededa0364baa8c1233a6f14df80c21f60a41","tid":2723,"uid":11310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:19:17.000Z","msg":"人工幾錢？"},{"pid":"